              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " I share a similar sentiment, licensing as the only theory of change seems unlikely to materially change things.  I think "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://jacobin.com/2016/02/free-software-movement-richard-stallman-linux-open-source-enclosure/",
                "text": "this essay"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " articulates it the best I've seen."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
